<hymn_number>38</hymn_number>
<title>MOA JESOSY VE TSY AHY ? ASAFA38</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Na mandalo ady sarotra aza aho
 Moa Jesosy ve tsy ahy ?
 Aroko sy mandako, sady tokiko
 Na hisesy eo anoloako aza moa
 'Zay mety ho fakam-panahy
 Mampandresy ahy hatrany Jeso.

[C1]
   Izy no namonjy ahy
   Ka nanafaka ahy
   Ary koa mbola miaro
   Sy hitantana ahy
   Na hisesy eo anoloako aza moa
   'Zay mety ho fakam-panahy
   Mampandresy ahy hatrany Jeso.

[V2]
 Na ambinina aza ireo ratsy fanahy
 Moa Jesosy ve tsy ahy ?
 Tsy mba hierikerika aho
 Tsy hanana ahiahy
 Na ety an-tany na any an-danitra any
 Ts'isy iriko tahaka Azy
 Vatolampy sy anjarako Izy

[C2]
   Izy no namonjy ahy
   Ka nanafaka ahy
   Ary koa mbola miaro
   Sy hitantana ahy
   Na ety an-tany na any an-danitra any
   Ts'isy iriko tahaka Azy
   Vatolampy sy anjarako Izy</lyrics>
</song>